PN,31501
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1780783874
OL,3,CNew AI tool which colour-codes the
OL,4,Cbody during live surgery used in UK-
OL,5,Cfirst
OL,7,FA new AI tool which colour-codes
OL,8,Fdifferent parts of the body during
OL,9,Flive operations has been used by
OL,10,Fsurgeons for the first time in the UK.
OL,12,FMedics at St Mark's, the National
OL,13,FBowel Hospital, used the tool to
OL,14,Foperate on a patient in her 60s on
OL,15,FThursday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1780783874
OL,3,CNew AI tool which colour-codes the
OL,4,Cbody during live surgery used in UK-
OL,5,Cfirst
OL,7,FThe tool, which is used alongside
OL,8,Frobotic or laparoscopic surgery,
OL,9,Fhighlights different parts of the
OL,10,Fanatomy in real time on a screen,
OL,11,Fhelping surgeons as they protect or
OL,12,Fdissect certain parts of the body
OL,13,Fduring their operations.
OL,15,FFor instance, connective tissue could
OL,16,Fbe highlighted as turquoise or nerves
OL,17,Fcould be highlighted in green, and
OL,18,Fother parts of the anatomy can be
OL,19,Fhighlighted with other colours.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1780783874
OL,3,CNew AI tool which colour-codes the
OL,4,Cbody during live surgery used in UK-
OL,5,Cfirst
OL,7,FExperts said the tool, known as the
OL,8,FEureka system, helps precision,
OL,9,Fefficiency and safety.
OL,11,FThe portable AI unit was developed by
OL,12,Fsurgeons in Japan who trained the tool
OL,13,Fusing thousands of videos of surgical
OL,14,Fprocedures.
OL,16,FThe operation on Thursday was the
OL,17,Ffirst time it has been used in the UK.
OL,19,FIt was also the first time that it has
OL,20,Fbeen used during surgery outside Japan.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1780783874
OL,3,CNew AI tool which colour-codes the
OL,4,Cbody during live surgery used in UK-
OL,5,Cfirst
OL,7,FThe patient, who has not been named,
OL,8,Freceived a bowel resection at the
OL,9,Fhospital, which is part of London
OL,10,FNorth West University Healthcare NHS
OL,11,FTrust.
OL,13,FConsultant surgeon Mr Kapil Sahnan
OL,14,Fdescribed the tool as an "extra
OL,15,Fhelping arm".
OL,17,FHe told the Press Association that it
OL,18,Fhelps "look at your live surgery and
OL,19,Fstart telling you which are the hidden
OL,20,Fstructures which perhaps you can't
OL,21,Fsee".
OL,26,@vD@ZOUwD@LO]zD@GOU}D@DO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1780783874
OL,3,CNew AI tool which colour-codes the
OL,4,Cbody during live surgery used in UK-
OL,5,Cfirst
OL,7,FHe added: "And the hope and the idea
OL,8,Fbeing is, that if you can identify
OL,9,Fthese, that the operation becomes
OL,10,Fsafer, you have this kind of extra
OL,11,Fhelping arm with artificial
OL,12,Fintelligence running at the same time
OL,13,Fas your surgery, preventing errors and
OL,14,Fmaking everything a lot more safe.
OL,16,F"And we were the first hospital in the
OL,17,Fworld outside of Japan to use it."
OL,26,@oD@KOUxD@AOUyD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1780783874
OL,3,CNew AI tool which colour-codes the
OL,4,Cbody during live surgery used in UK-
OL,5,Cfirst
OL,7,FHe went on: "Another way of thinking
OL,8,Fabout it is, I remember that my mother
OL,9,Fused to use an A to Z when she had to
OL,10,Fplan routes. Now we all use Google
OL,11,FMaps and Waze.
OL,13,F"And this is that version of kind of
OL,14,Fnavigation that now has been applied
OL,15,Fto surgery.
OL,17,F"The difference has been that real
OL,18,Ftime aspect, so you can see it at the
OL,19,Fsame time as you're operating.
OL,26,@oD@MOUuD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1780783874
OL,3,CNew AI tool which colour-codes the
OL,4,Cbody during live surgery used in UK-
OL,5,Cfirst
OL,7,F"The idea being is you want to prevent
OL,8,Fany errors happening before they do,
OL,9,Fand one way to do that is use, not
OL,10,Fhuman intelligence but intelligence,
OL,11,Fwhich has been derived from thousands
OL,12,Fand thousands and thousands of
OL,13,Foperative videos where people have
OL,14,Fgone through and labelled things.
OL,16,F"So the computer can see things before
OL,17,Fthe human eye can."
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@AOUyD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1780783874
OL,3,CNew AI tool which colour-codes the
OL,4,Cbody during live surgery used in UK-
OL,5,Cfirst
OL,7,FHe added: "You get these really
OL,8,Fbeautiful images, they put colour
OL,9,Foverlays over the operative images,
OL,10,Fwhich can either be on constantly, or
OL,11,Fthey can pulse."
OL,13,FMr Sahnan said work was under way to
OL,14,Fwork out how "we can genuinely prove
OL,15,Fthat this is going to be advantageous
OL,16,Fand, more importantly, how we can
OL,17,Fstart rolling it out.
OL,26,@oD@KOUsD@PO]vD@NOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1780783874
OL,3,CNew AI tool which colour-codes the
OL,4,Cbody during live surgery used in UK-
OL,5,Cfirst
OL,7,F"We're lucky to have it today, but it
OL,8,Fwould be amazing if everybody had it
OL,9,Fin the next couple of years, it would
OL,10,Fmake surgery for everybody a lot
OL,11,Fsafer."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/9
